title: Ed Sheeran credits his dad with keeping him grounded during epic success - Evesham Journal
text:
Brit-winning singer Ed Sheeran credited his father for keeping him grounded at the world premiere of his tour documentary, Jumpers For Goalposts. The Thinking Out Loud star, 24, said his strict dad John would ensure he never gets too caught up with fame.
 Evesham Journal.
